Description: A focused launcher for your desktop
 Vicinae is a modern, keyboard-driven application launcher for Linux
 desktops. It provides quick access to applications, files, and system
 functions through an elegant and customizable interface.
 .
 Features include:
  - Fast application launching
  - Browser extension integration
  - Wayland and X11 support
  - Customizable themes
  - Extension support via TypeScript/React
